Tombs & Mummies

by Matthew Warner

Your arch enemy, having stolen your girlfriend, throws you down through a hole in the ceiling. You have landed in the underground tomb of the Pharaoh Haputet."Have fun staying with the king . . . for eternity!" he says before closing a hatch over the hole. Your way out is somewhere in this tomb. Watch out for hazards!

The Entry Room
You can see a torch.
You can go up.
It's too dark to see much other than the faint outline of the hatch far above you.
> ignite torch

> ignite torch
You use a match to ignite the torch. Its flickering flames reveal much.
The torch has an old, dry wick. It's ancient, after all. Keep an eye on your "Torch Wick" status. When it reaches 0, you'll need to re-light it.
> take torch

> take torch
You pick it up.
