The Shrine of Thoth
You can see the Ark of Magic.
You can go west or north.
Thoth was the god of divine words, magic, wisdom, and the moon. A mural shows the beak-faced Thoth writing on a tablet.

> open chest

> open chest
You open it.
It contains a papyrus and a Cloak of Protection.
