The Shrine of Anubis
You can see a Flail of Anubis.
You can go south or west.
A mural of Anubis, jackal god of embalming and the dead, wraps around the walls. You might expect to find this in the burial chamber, wherever that might be, but the Egyptians must have had another reason to place it here.

> take flail

> take flail
You take it.
> w

